    "content": "<h1 id=\"statistical-performance-metadata\">Statistical performance metadata<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#statistical-performance-metadata\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h1>\n<p>Metadata for a selection of indicators from the World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. 2023. Source: <a href=\"https://www.worldbank.org/en/programs/statistical-performance-indicators\">https://www.worldbank.org/en/programs/statistical-performance-indicators</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"census\">Census<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#census\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"population-housing-census\">Population \\&amp; Housing census<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#population-housing-census\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>stats-census-population</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Population censuses collect data on the size, distribution and composition of population and information on a broad range of social and economic characteristics of the population.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown or n.a.; 1=No census done within last 20 years; 2=Census done within last 20 years; 3=Census done within last 10 years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Original scoring: 1 Point. Population census done within last 10 years. 0.5 Points. Population census done within last 20 years. 0 Points. Otherwise</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Data Collection Guidelines</td>\n<td>From World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. Series SPI.D4.1.1.POPU</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"agriculture-census\">Agriculture census<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#agriculture-census\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>stats-census-agriculture</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Agriculture censuses collect information on agricultural activities, such as size of holding, land tenure, land use, employment and production, and provide basic structural data and sampling frames for agricultural surveys.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown or n.a.; 1=No census done within last 20 years; 2=Census done within last 20 years; 3=Census done within last 10 years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Original scoring: 1 Point. census done within last 10 years. 0.5 Points. census done within last 20 years. 0 Points. Otherwise</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Data Collection Guidelines</td>\n<td>From World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. Series SPI.D4.1.2.AGRI</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"businessestablishment-census\">Business/establishment census<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#businessestablishment-census\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>stats-census-business</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Business/establishment censuses provide valuable information on all economic activities, number of employed and size of establishments in the economy.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown or n.a.; 1=No census done within last 20 years; 2=Census done within last 20 years; 3=Census done within last 10 years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Original scoring: 1 Point. census done within last 10 years. 0.5 Points. census done within last 20 years. 0 Points. Otherwise</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Data Collection Guidelines</td>\n<td>From World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. Series SPI.D4.1.3.BIZZ</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"survey\">Survey<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#survey\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"household-survey-on-income-etc\">Household Survey on income, etc<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#household-survey-on-income-etc\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>stats-survey-household</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>These surveys collect data on household income (including income in kind), consumption and expenditure.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown or n.a.; 1=No survey done within last 10 years; 2=1 survey done within past 10 years; 3=2 surveys done within past 10 years; 4=3 or more surveys done within last 10 years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Original scoring: 1 Point. 3 or more surveys done within past 10 years. 0.6 Points. 2 surveys done within past 10 years. 0.3 Points. 1 survey done within past 10 years. 0 Points. None within past 10 years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Data Collection Guidelines</td>\n<td>From World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. Series SPI.D4.1.4.HOUS</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"agriculture-survey\">Agriculture survey<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#agriculture-survey\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>stats-survey-agriculture</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Agricultural surveys refer to surveys of agricultural holdings based on the sampling frames established by the agricultural census.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown or n.a.; 1=No survey done within last 10 years; 2=1 survey done within past 10 years; 3=2 surveys done within past 10 years; 4=3 or more surveys done within last 10 years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Original scoring: 1 Point. 3 or more surveys done within past 10 years. 0.6 Points. 2 surveys done within past 10 years. 0.3 Points. 1 survey done within past 10 years. 0 Points. None within past 10 years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Data Collection Guidelines</td>\n<td>From World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. Series SPI.D4.1.5.AGSVY</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"labor-force-survey\">Labor Force Survey<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#labor-force-survey\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>stats-survey-labour</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Labor force survey is a standard household-based survey of work-related statistics at the national and sub-national employment or unemployment levels, rates or trends.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown or n.a.; 1=No survey done within last 10 years; 2=1 survey done within past 10 years; 3=2 surveys done within past 10 years; 4=3 or more surveys done within last 10 years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Original scoring: 1 Point. 3 or more surveys done within past 10 years. 0.6 Points. 2 surveys done within past 10 years. 0.3 Points. 1 survey done within past 10 years. 0 Points. None within past 10 years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Data Collection Guidelines</td>\n<td>From World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. Series SPI.D4.1.6.LABR</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"healthdemographic-survey\">Health/Demographic survey<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#healthdemographic-survey\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>stats-survey-health</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Health surveys collect information on various aspects of health of populations, such as health expenditure, access, utilization, and outcomes.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown or n.a.; 1=No survey done within last 10 years; 2=1 survey done within past 10 years; 3=2 surveys done within past 10 years; 4=3 or more surveys done within last 10 years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Original scoring: 1 Point. 3 or more surveys done within past 10 years. 0.6 Points. 2 surveys done within past 10 years. 0.3 Points. 1 survey done within past 10 years. 0 Points. None within past 10 years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Data Collection Guidelines</td>\n<td>From World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. Series SPI.D4.1.7.HLTH</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"businessestablishment-survey\">Business/establishment survey<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#businessestablishment-survey\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>stats-survey-business</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>The business/establishment survey provides information on employment, hours, and earnings of employees from a sample of business establishments including private and public, entities that are classified based on an establishment's principal activity from the business or establishment census.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown or n.a.; 1=No survey done within last 10 years; 2=1 survey done within past 10 years; 3=2 surveys done within past 10 years; 4=3 or more surveys done within last 10 years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Original scoring: 1 Point. 3 or more surveys done within past 10 years. 0.6 Points. 2 surveys done within past 10 years. 0.3 Points. 1 survey done within past 10 years. 0 Points. None within past 10 years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Data Collection Guidelines</td>\n<td>From World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. Series SPI.D4.1.8.BZSVY</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"score\">Score<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#score\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"data-use-score\">Data Use - Score<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#data-use-score\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>stats-score-use</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Indicators that capture demand side of statistical system</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown or n.a.; 1=&lt;20%; 2=20-49%;3=50-69%; 4=70-89%; 5=&gt;89%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Original scoring: Weighted average of statistical performance indicators related to data services. Scores range from 0-100 with 100 representing the best score.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Data Collection Guidelines</td>\n<td>From World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. Series SPI.INDEX.PIL1</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"data-services-score\">Data Services - Score<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#data-services-score\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>stats-score-service</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Information on data releases, online access, and other data services</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown or n.a.; 1=&lt;20%; 2=20-49%;3=50-69%; 4=70-89%; 5=&gt;89%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Original scoring: Weighted average of statistical performance indicators related to data services. Scores range from 0-100 with 100 representing the best score.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Data Collection Guidelines</td>\n<td>From World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. Series SPI.INDEX.PIL2</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"data-products-score\">Data Products - Score<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#data-products-score\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>stats-score-products</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Whether the country is able to produce relevant indicators, primarily related to SDGs</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown or n.a.; 1=&lt;20%; 2=20-49%;3=50-69%; 4=70-89%; 5=&gt;89%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Original scoring: Weighted average of statistical performance indicators related to data products. Scores range from 0-100 with 100 representing the best score.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Data Collection Guidelines</td>\n<td>From World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. Series SPI.INDEX.PIL3</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"data-sources-score\">Data Sources - Score<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#data-sources-score\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>stats-score-sources</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Censuses and surveys, admin data, geospatial</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown or n.a.; 1=&lt;20%; 2=20-49%;3=50-69%; 4=70-89%; 5=&gt;89%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Original scoring: Weighted average of statistical performance indicators related to data sources. Scores range from 0-100 with 100 representing the best score.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Data Collection Guidelines</td>\n<td>From World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. Series SPI.INDEX.PIL4</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"data-infrastructure-score\">Data Infrastructure - Score<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#data-infrastructure-score\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>stats-score-infrastructure</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Standards and methodology used in classification</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown or n.a.; 1=&lt;20%; 2=20-49%;3=50-69%; 4=70-89%; 5=&gt;89%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Original scoring: Weighted average of statistical performance indicators related to data infrastructure. Scores range from 0-100 with 100 representing the best score.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Data Collection Guidelines</td>\n<td>From World Bank Statistical Performance Indicators. Series SPI.INDEX.PIL5</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
